<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>

<head>
    <title>New Adoption Request</title>
</head>

<body>
    <h1>New Adoption Request for <%= petName %>
    </h1>
    <p>Hello <%= listerName %>,</p>
    <p>You have received a new adoption request for your listed pet, <strong>
            <%= petName %>
        </strong>, from <strong>
            <%= adopterName %>
        </strong>.</p>
    <p>You can view the details and manage the request here:</p>
    <p><a href="<%= requestUrl %>">Manage Pet Listing</a></p>
    <p>Thank you,<br>The PawPal Team</p>
</body>

</html>